ource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With one apparatus - floor exercise - to go, Yulo totes a 68.699 total.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo makes a huge leap in the standings and climbs to joint 12th through four apparatuses as he earns 14.500 points in parallel bars.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1162, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo has a 55.099 total so far.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Up next for Yulo is horizontal bar and floor exercise.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1349, \"end\": 1353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.419401502779009e-40, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo shines in one of his pet events, garnering 14.766 points in vault.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He lands a front handspring double pike with a half twist as Yulo posts his highest score through his first three apparatuses.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Total so far: 40.599 points.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pumping both of his fists out of satisfaction after his performance, Carlos Yulo bounces back in still rings and nets 13.933 points.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo improves on his score of 13.000 in the qualification.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His total after two apparatuses is 25.833.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo opens the all-around final on pommel horse and gets 11.900 points after a routine marred by a fall.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo can bring his total score up in the other five apparatuses.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlo Paalam is a win away from a guaranteed medal as he advances to the quarterfinals of the men's 57kg class after a unanimous decision victory over Ireland's Jude Gallagher.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlo_Paalam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlo Paalam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlo_Paalam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlo_Paalam\"}, {\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2206, \"title\": \"