nga is the second Filipino boxer to get eliminated afterEumir Marcial.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2692, \"end\": 2699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Igorot_people\", \"score\": 0.9999032074491729, \"rank\": 9.230043661988316e-05, \"text\": \"Kalinga\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Igorot_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Igorot_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read the full storyhere.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Joanie Delgaco falls to the classification final D in the women's single sculls after placing fifth in her semifinal C/D race with a time of 8:00.18.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2794, \"end\": 2800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Caucus\", \"score\": 0.5797512083252878, \"rank\": 0.72487781938143, \"text\": \"Joanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Caucus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Caucus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Delgaco will vie for the 19th to 24th places in the final D.  Only the top three rowers advance to the final C, where the 13th to 18th places will be contended.\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read the full storyhere.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kayla Sanchez bows out of the Olympics as she misses the top-eight cutoff for the final of the women's 100m freestyle.\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Sanchez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kayla Sanchez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Sanchez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Sanchez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sanchez finishes 15th out of the 16 semifinalis